---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import AICounsellor from "../components/AICounsellor";
import { ShieldCheck, Lock, EyeOff, Server, HardDrive, Key, ArrowLeft } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout 
  title="Security Audit | TESCA Global Advisory Platform"
  description="Explore our ISO 27001 data compliance framework, document vault encryption, database security audits, and privacy standards."
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 pt-8 pb-12 text-left">
    
    <!-- Go Back Link -->
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-accent-blue hover:underline mb-8 font-sans">
      <ArrowLeft class="w-4 h-4" /> Back to Home
    </a>

    <!-- Premium Header Banner -->
    <div class="glass-card rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-slate-50/80 border border-slate-200/60 shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 relative mb-12">
      <div class="aurora-bg w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-accent-blue/5 -top-12 -left-12 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6 relative z-10">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-800 bg-accent-blue/10 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-accent-blue/20 font-sans uppercase">
          Security Auditing & Compliance
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-[36px] sm:text-[48px] lg:text-[56px] font-extrabold font-display text-support-white tracking-tight leading-none">
          Data Security & Systems Audit
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-[18px] text-support-gray font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed">
          TESCA enforces institutional-grade data security protocols. We audit our client documentation vaults weekly to guarantee complete compliance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Security Pillars -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50/70 border border-blue-100 space-y-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-3 rounded-2xl bg-white text-accent-blue inline-block shadow-sm">
          <Lock class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-display">AES-256 Encryption</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          All client files, transcripts, passport copies, and statements are fully encrypted at rest and in transit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50/70 border border-purple-100 space-y-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-3 rounded-2xl bg-white text-purple-600 inline-block shadow-sm">
          <EyeOff class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-display">RBAC Data Access</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          Strict Role-Based Access Controls mean only your matching, verified visa consultant can review your files.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50/70 border border-emerald-100 space-y-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-3 rounded-2xl bg-white text-emerald-600 inline-block shadow-sm">
          <Server class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-display">ISO 27001 Standards</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          Our servers and workflows follow ISO 27001 (Information Security Management System) principles.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Audit Details -->
    <div class="space-y-12 max-w-4xl font-sans">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-display tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2">
          <Key class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-blue" /> 1. Encryption Keys & Key Management
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          TESCA utilizes automated key rotation algorithms. Master keys are kept in secure physical key vaults separated from the secondary databases containing metadata. This structure protects candidate records from brute force or network interception vectors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-display tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2">
          <HardDrive class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-blue" /> 2. Document Retention & Purge Cycles
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          Following visa approval and program commencement, all sensitive applicant records (financial receipts, passports, transcript backups) are securely wiped from our online databases after 90 days. We preserve only standard accounting ledgers and university tracking codes offline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 font-display tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2">
          <ShieldCheck class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-blue" /> 3. External Penetration Audits
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          Our platform undergoes external penetration testing twice a year. Audit statements verify complete firewall security against injection, cross-site scripting, and credential exploitation. Our verified ISO certification confirms zero security leaks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <AICounsellor client:load />
</Layout>
